message.raw:
Adding PyCapture2 Camera Server to Bitbucket

This file contains a command line camera server for
Pointgrey/FLIR usb3 cameras. It optionally utilizes
the new acquistion_ROI property of the camera class.
To start the server, type "python PyCapture2_camera
_server.py <cameraNameFromBlacs>" in a command line
running in the labscript_utils directory.

DSB
